description.narrative:
The overall objective of the project is support to reinvigorate the RC to accelerate SDG implementation in Zimbabwe, through seven broad pillars: 
1) joint UN support to the Government to prepare and implement the new national development plan; 
2) consolidation of the investments towards gender equality; 
3) joint UN prevention strategy for sustaining peace and promoting human rights; 
4) strategic communication and advocacy for UN values and principles; 
5) joint UN support to increase transparency and accountability to fight corruption; 
6) strengthening humanitarian-development nexus, including through coordinated Disaster Risk Reduction and Climate Action efforts; and
7) strengthening sectoral and multi-sectoral coordination across key strategic priority areas to maximize results.
